{"tid":2235374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"左膠們，究竟係\"已死\"定\"陣痛\"，唔該你地搞好個邏輯同定位至好帶風向","createTime":"2020-10-08T15:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T07:48:03.000Z","uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76e0e477acb6f1bbb117b670cb4e54a9be734a86","tid":2235374,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:22:10.000Z","msg":"已死=玩完=破滅=爛咗=死亡=the end=game over<br />\n<br />\n解決方法：唔玩！走佬、放棄、認輸<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">重生？唔係香港人主導到既範圍</span><br />\n<br />\n陣痛=痛苦過程=低潮=一段時期既亂局<br />\n<br />\n應對方法：捱一段時間、可期待黑暗之後既光明、做好準備期待新既機會<br />\n<br />\n認同係已死，就冇可能係陣痛，認同陣痛就唔會係已死，如果話係長期既陣痛，例如最少有十年八年，咁等同已死冇分別，你無謂用陣痛之名黎呃人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人可以係已死既地方同時期都可以好好生存甚至搵大錢，呢個係個人既運氣同佢本事，唔可以放落一般大眾市民身上黎講<br />\n陣痛至有重生之機會，死亡係唔會有，因為死咗，所有野重新做過係全世界人不可預知既，除非你係神，你又唔係<br />\n已死同陣痛，只有其一，咪同我講十年陣痛，不如你十年唔食野唔飲水都未死再出黎帶風向，啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae855c8d5ecf420c2476a53b1fcba44b6c2ba31b","tid":2235374,"uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"日日都運動已死架啦已經聽到悶<br />\n<br />\n一睇到呢四隻字就搵返呢個PO出黎就岩架啦<br />\n以前蘇聯KGB玩撚到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n遊行無用，勇武無用，連儂牆無用，民意開始逆轉，開始攰，好想死，仲唔散係弱智，仲唔衝係嘥氣，條例已經死亡，警察已經內鬨<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2176267\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2176267</a>"},{"pid":"aa37efea19d34b431f1254e2bf4942d8daa329b6","tid":2235374,"uid":60665,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"係已死/game over<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係永不超生嗰隻"},{"pid":"714e5c24e6c52ce68521187c1dc883cc4089bf32","tid":2235374,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa37efea19d34b431f1254e2bf4942d8daa329b6","tid":2235374,"uid":60665,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"係已死/game over<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係永不超生嗰隻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T22:55:33.000Z","msg":"泛民左膠主導，必死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b39a316ee1580b2fe0c1d979d1385315d2601e4","tid":2235374,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa37efea19d34b431f1254e2bf4942d8daa329b6","tid":2235374,"uid":60665,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"係已死/game over<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係永不超生嗰隻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T22:58:00.000Z","msg":"睇美國同梵蒂岡就知啦<br />\n<br />\n中共21世紀將稱霸世界"},{"pid":"3e95735b235a57bb94d8f21d479c048b9300a9d4","tid":2235374,"uid":37525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T01:06:38.000Z","msg":"死咗可以投胎 =返生"},{"pid":"a66a57d77c32189cdb8b1ef55148f3b11ca30361","tid":2235374,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-11T16:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b22ad5bb3c82bd66914082d43f34f116e3b48ff","tid":2235374,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}